# raw/ — Drop Zone

Drop any unstructured material here: articles, notes, screenshots (as text), PDFs (as text exports),
meeting notes, bookmarks, research, competitor data, voice note transcripts.

Rules:
- CoreMind NEVER edits files in raw/ — these are your single source of truth
- CoreMind NEVER deletes from raw/ without asking you
- Filename format: anything goes — don't organize manually, CoreMind owns that

To ingest: "Ingest new raw files, update wiki/ articles, suggest new topics"
